linemodels R-package, ChangeLog

v.0.4.0 (10-July-2024)
- Added possibility to analyze more than 2 dimensions,
   which required changes to existing functions.
   Input formats of v.0.3.0 should still work.
- Added multiple new functions.

v.0.3.0 (20-Nov-2023)
- Added simulate.loglr( )
- Added simulate.linemodels.for.observations( )
- Modified line.models.optimize( )
  * Added option 'print.steps' to control console output from optimization steps
  * Added possibility to optimize only the proportion parameters


v.0.2.1 (07-Aug-2023)

### Fixed
- A minor bug in the convergence criteria check of the optimization algorithm.


v.0.2.0 (15-Jan-2023)

### Added
- visualize.classification.regions( )

### Fixed
- EM-algorithm to optimize line model parameters


v.0.1.0 (05-Oct-2022)

First version release.
